Title: Attack on Teotia an act of revenge by cousins: Police
Content: The attack on BJP leader Brijpal Teotia last week was carried out by two cousins from his native village to avenge a family member’s killing 17 years ago, the Uttar Pradesh Police claimed on Wednesda
Author: Mohammad Ali
